de.fhg.fokus.restac.httpx.core.common
Class HTTPStatus

java.lang.Object
  de.fhg.fokus.restac.httpx.core.common.HTTPStatus

public class HTTPStatus
extends java.lang.Object

Stores the status code and reason phrase of an HTTP response as defined in RFC 2616.

Author:
Philippe Bößling, Stefan Föll
See Also:
href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2616.txt" target="_blank">RFC 2616
